songs.title: Charso Bees
songs.lyrics:
CHARSO BEES,CHA-CHARSO BEES,CHA-CHARSO BEES,CHARSO BEES,CHARSO BEES
CHA-CHARSO BEES,CHA-CHARSO BEES,CHARSO BEES,CHARSO BEES,CHA-CHARSO BEES
CHA-CHARSO BEES,CHARSO BEES,CHARSO BEES,CHA-CHARSO BEES,...YEAH

BOHEMIA MAIN JADON DA AAYA,VE MAINU ROKAN CHALE KINE KOI ROK NA PAYA,VE MAINE SARI DUNIYA CH NAA KAMAYA,VE LOKI BOLDE VE AAPAN KARKE VAKHAYA,VE JAKE UK WICH KUDIYAN TE KARAN JADU,VE BACK STAGE MAINU MILAN AAYA BALLY SAGOO
VE BBC WALE PUCHDE SAWAAL KINE,VE CTV TE RAJA BAITHA DUJE DIN,VE MUMBAI AAKE KITI MAINE AISH KINI,VE BHANG THODI PITI,KITI MAINE AISH KINI,SAWERE NASHIYAN CH UTHEYA MAIN DER NAAL,VE RATI SHOW MERA DELHI CH DALER NAAL
VE AAPAN SOLAN AANE BAKI SARE MUNDE JALI,KALI DENALI WICH FIRE RAJA RAAT SARI,VE DESI HIPHOP DA CHA HUN SAREYAN NU,PAR JADON RAJA KARE RAP MAIDAN KHALI....

RAJA HARJAI CHARSO BEES,GALI GALI CH MUNDE KARAN MERI REES
RAJA HARJAI CHARSO BEES,YEAH CHARSO BEES,CHARSO BEES....

CHARSO BEES,CHARSO BEES,CHA-CHARSO BEES,CHA-CHARSO BEES
CHARSO BEES,HAN.........

HUN NAVAN DIN,NAVI DUNIYA DI TOR,JHUTHE YAARAN TOH MAIN DOOR,MERI JEBI PAISA HOR,SARI DUNIYA CH SHOW KARAN SARE MAINU JANDE,PAR BORDER PATROL MAINU CANADA NI AAN DEN,PEHLI CD MAIN CHAPI DO HAZAR WARI
DUJI CD MAIN VECHI DO SO HAZAR WARI,MUQABALA NI JAG CH MERA
MERI TIJI CD DA NAA " DA RAP STAR ",MAINU UNIVERSAL WALE DENDE TANKHA,BALLY SAGOO UK TOH MAINU BHEJE PAISA NASHA PAYAR,VEKH YAARAN DI BADLI ROOH
SALE LABDE BAHANE MAINU KARAN CHALE SU,MAINU KOI PAYE NI ROK,VE NALE COURT CH BAITHE MAIN LUTANA NI NOTE,VE MERE JAIL YAAR,LIKHAN YAARAN NU TASLIYAN KABARASTAAN MERE DUSHMANA DI GALIYAN.....
